mixin delivery-methods
  .delivery-methods&attributes(attributes)
    ul.delivery-methods__list
      li.delivery-methods__item.delivery-methods__item--courier
        input.delivery-methods__control.visually-hidden(id='courier-delivery-method-control' type='radio' name='delivery-method' value='courier' data-type='courier')
        label.delivery-methods__label.delivery-methods__label--courier(for='courier-delivery-method-control') Курьером
          span.delivery-methods__text 499 ₽
        button.delivery-methods__button(type='button' data-modal-opener='address-form') Ввести адрес
      li.delivery-methods__item.delivery-methods__item--point
        input.delivery-methods__control.visually-hidden(id='pick-up-point-delivery-method-control' type='radio' name='delivery-method' value='pick-up-point' data-type='point')
        label.delivery-methods__label.delivery-methods__label--point(for='pick-up-point-delivery-method-control') До ПВЗ
          span.delivery-methods__text 699 ₽
        button.delivery-methods__button.delivery-methods__button--sdek-point(type='button' data-modal-opener='sdek-sdek') Выбрать ПВЗ
        button.delivery-methods__button.delivery-methods__button--post-point(type='button' data-modal-opener='sdek-post') Выбрать ПВЗ
